@startuml NotificationsCommunication
left to right direction

actor "User" as user
actor "Instructor" as instructor
actor "System" as system
actor "SMTP Server" as smtp

rectangle "Notifications & Communication System" {
  usecase "Send Notification" as UC0701
  usecase "Log Event" as log_event
  usecase "Send Email" as UC0702
  usecase "Private Messaging" as UC0703
  usecase "Validate Recipient" as validate_recipient
  usecase "Manage Preferences" as UC0704
  usecase "Mark as Read" as UC0705
}

' Actor Associations
system --> UC0701 : **Association**
system --> UC0702 : **Association**
user --> UC0703 : **Association**
user --> UC0704 : **Association**
user --> UC0705 : **Association**
instructor --> UC0703 : **Association**
smtp --> UC0702 : **Association**

' Use Case Relationships
UC0701 ..> log_event : **<<include>>**
UC0702 ..> UC0701 : **<<extend>>**
UC0703 ..> validate_recipient : **<<include>>**

@enduml